item.dc:creator: @_BBLLAARRGGHH __--BBLLAARRGGHH--__
item.description:
@_BBLLAARRGGHH wrote:

[quote=“lesterknome, post:49, topic:318106”][quote author=Jc22493 link=topic=414614.msg3052985#msg3052985 date=1260224213]

my parents gave up on my a long time ago.

dont worry you get over it

They did give up on me. the funny thing is, (they even told me this many times) they are just trying to my life a living hell for me making theirs hell. But i can give a hit better then i take one

Oo yes, same with me. I smell revenge?

meh, they have nothing to take from me anymore so i might as well fuck up their life (Email there boss porn [i know my mom’s email] ect)

But have you thought about the consequences of doing that? Your mom has a chance of losing her job, which means that there is less income for the household. Although your mom returned your computer, took away your materialistic belongings, and so on, she’s still providing food and shelter for you, is she not? Think twice before ranting about your parents. They’re the ones that raised you. If it were not for your ‘fucked-up’ parents, where would your Christmas gift have come from originally? Where would your college funds have come from? If it weren’t for them, you probably would not even have the ability to post on these forums, let alone live. Think about what your parents have provided you with rather than what they have taken away. The belongings they take away are composed of the things they have given you.
[/quote]

  1. their fault for forgetting a condom
  2. I pay for my own college funds
  3. My mom barely makes me food, she makes it for my dad and i eat the left overs
  4. they never take me out[/quote]
    I think over exaggeration here. You get the leftovers? Either this is a lie, or child services are needed.

item.dc:creator: @runefreak10 runefreak10
item.description:
@runefreak10 wrote:

[quote="`Lewk_, post:45, topic:318106"][quote author=runefreak10 link=topic=414614.msg3052868#msg3052868 date=1260219315]

Fuckin’ run away. If you have a really close friend where their parents love you, go there.

You’re a fucking tool, that solves nothing. They are going to find you no matter what. I don’t think you’re friends parents are just gonna let you stay at their house.

How the fuck does that justify me being a tool? Aaaaaaaand, if I was that kid I wouldn’t take the shit. I’ve ran away before and gone to my friend’s house. They would let you stay at their house if you’re close to them and they’re like your second parents.
[/quote]
Where else are they gonna search? Of course your friends house, you aren’t going to sleep in the bus station… They’re (cops) going to search your friends house… I believe the jew hunt has been over for a while now. Sure you’ll say “oh what if my friend’s parents say no you can’t search my house”, I bet if you parents cared enough they’d get a warrant. It’s a retarded idea none the less, like you said. You ran away, you came back. It doesn’t solve anything. It just wastes everyones time to search for a decaying piece of organic matter that your parents may or may not call “theirs”. Just fucking deal with it. Pussies run away.[/quote]

You run away to get out of the house, and frankly, it helped me. So it wasn’t a waste of time. My parents knew where I was anyways. It doesn’t make me a pussy to want out of dramatic bullshit all the time. I’m not gonna fucking deal with it if I don’t have to.
